Package author: Igor Gaponenko

Please describe any modifications that you made to the package in the
reverse time order.

Tag: V00-01-07
2015-04-23 Igor Gaponenko
- extended widget CheckTable to allow registering a callback function
on changes made to the object state
- moved _ASSERT and _PROP methods which are used to parse widget configuration
options from CheckTable into it sbase class Widget. This will allow using
these methods from any derived widgets.
- added three new widgets: Checkbox, SelectOption and TextInput. The widgets
allow to be configured with an optional persistent state backend (to save
teh state on each change and to restore it upon an initialization).
- fixed a minor bug in the Framework

Tag: V00-01-06
2015-04-16 Igor Gaponenko
- fixed a memory leak bug in SmartTable widget
- added a test for memory leaks
- improved styling for tooltips

Tag: V00-01-05
2015-03-10 Igor Gaponenko
- added group headers and fancy annotation to the PropList widget
- added another demo for SmartTable widget

Tag: V00-01-04
2015-02-26 Igor Gaponenko
- minor changes in CSS (size and colors)

Tag: V00-01-03
2014-12-08 Igor Gaponenko
- minor changes in CSS (fonts)

Tag: V00-01-02
2014-10-24 Igor Gaponenko
- new dynamuically loadable module SimpleTable to replace Table as per JIRA
ticket PSWA-16. Also added a test for the new class.
- extended FwkApplication to be aware about its "path": application/tab name,
context1, and context2 (when last two are awailable)
- minor modification to the CSS loading mechanism to prevent pages from
styaing in browser caches forever as per JIRA ticket PSWA-14

Tag: V00-01-01
2014-10-10 Igor Gaponenko
- code cleanup
- smart table widget
- continued RequireJS migration
- minor extention to the Fwk API

Tag: V00-01-00
2014-05-21 Igor Gaponenko
- imajor refactoring to migrate to the component model based on RequireJS (AMD)

